<h1 class="mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how <strong>Homeix</strong> collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our website and services.</p>

<h2 class="mt-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and other details you provide when registering or contacting us.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you interact with our website, including pages visited, time spent, and preferences.</li>
    <li><strong>Cookies & Tracking:</strong> Small files stored on your device to enhance your browsing experience and analyze traffic.</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="mt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<ul>
    <li>To provide and maintain our services.</li>
    <li>To improve user experience and personalize content.</li>
    <li>To send updates, notifications, and promotional content (with your consent).</li>
    <li>To monitor and analyze usage trends to enhance our website and services.</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="mt-4">3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
<p>We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share information with trusted partners to help provide services, but only under strict confidentiality agreements.</p>

<h2 class="mt-4">4. Data Security</h2>
<p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.</p>

<h2 class="mt-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal data.</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent for marketing communications at any time.</li>
    <li>Request information about how your data is processed.</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="mt-4">6. Cookies</h2>
<p>We use cookies to improve website functionality and analyze traffic. You can control or disable cookies through your browser settings.</p>

<h2 class="mt-4">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated “Last Modified” date.</p>

<h2 class="mt-4">8. Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:info@homeix.com">info@homeix.com</a>.</p>

